data.description: If you have a large family, then you will love this 6 bedroom, 2 1/2 bath home in Farmington! Tons of living space, with beautiful hardwood floors, solid surface counters, a sunroom, privacy fenced yard, and garden shed. Located close to the schools, parks, and convenient for everything in town you need.  You will also enjoy the rear deck, and partially covered patio space for entertaining.
